{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, who would be interested in seeing my number, when people don't care that we are dying now?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The world stood silent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So Hitler was not alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the one who originated the idea, but people followed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why-- my mother was given orders too, and she risked her life and so did I.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I've learned about spiritual resistance, and I trust, and I know the spirit, because if the spirit is whole-- you know what my father once said to me?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Itka, people might break your heart, but no one can break your spirit, just yourself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you-- if you resist to evil, you will not break your spirit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Are there other things about Auschwitz that you--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About Auschwitz, I remembered constantly people dying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember everything was mountain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How there was-- I have some pictures later, I'll show you the mountains of the bodies laying, people they're using-- they had like little wagons-- I forgot what they're called-- to wheel the dead people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how people were trying-- how we felt all in the same boat, how we were constantly living in those conditions, and still hoping and still trying to hold onto the things that we believed, and helping each other.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were other things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, like when you, [INAUDIBLE] try to remember, sometimes you don't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you start talking about one, certain things come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyhow, we survived in Auschwitz 'til 1945, as I said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we came-- when we came to-- when we came, then there was no appel, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when we were chased out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't-- I didn't know the point if somebody left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found out later that some people were still left, the sick ones and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were driven on foot.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
